IMAPAccount lucas
Host mail.lucashorton.com 
User lucas@lucashorton.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.config/mbsync/mailpass.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore lucas-remote
Account lucas 

MaildirStore lucas-local
Path ~/.mail/lucas/
Inbox ~/.mail/lucas/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel lucas
Far :lucas-remote:
Near :lucas-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
